NOTE ON DATA LICENSING

This repository contains code only.  When the pipeline is run, it downloads
the VerSe 2019 / VerSe 2020 datasets from upstream sources; those datasets
are licensed under CC-BY-SA 4.0 by the original authors (Sekuboyina et al.,
Liebl & Schinz et al., Löffler et al.).  Any derivative datasets produced by
this pipeline (data/unified/, data/reoriented/, data/hf_export/, etc.)
inherit the CC-BY-SA 4.0 license and must be redistributed under the same
terms with appropriate attribution.
